$ A (very) simple webserver using the perl module HTTP::Server::Simple::CGI

The following webserver can be started using either
code {
./webserver.pl
code }
or
code {
./webserver.pl /path/to/document/root
code }


gh|PerlModules|/HTTP/Server/Simple/CGI/webserver.pl||

